title: Ep. #139 | Eric Nam's Thanksgiving Special~
description:
Hope you’re feeling thankful, because Eric is BACK this week for another solo episode! From a magical trip out to Dubai for Armani to dining with the cast of ‘Squid Game’ – OH, and releasing his new song ‘Any Other Way’ – Eric has A LOT to catch you up on! Hear what he has to say on this week’s special and also all the things that he’s thankful for in this season.

Get your tickets for Eric’s ‘There and Back Again’ world tour at https://ericnam.com
